{"type": "article", "id": 30353, "title": "球鞋展示架", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-31T22:57:03Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 39, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016073121084697i6clEXaR2MkKB8.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>对于鞋迷来说，封闭式的柜子的确能够提供一定的收纳空间，但却无法展示自己的珍贵收藏。最近美国波士顿的球鞋设计师 Jacob Garcia 将球鞋的三角形轮廓与鞋架巧妙地结合在一起，推出了一款名为 <a href=\"http://solestacks.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Sole Stacks</a> 的球鞋收纳系统。它有 6 和 10 层两种高度可选，除了放在地面之外还可以悬挂在墙上，提升了空间的利用率。鞋架的外框和搁板也提供了各种材质和颜色的订制选择，鞋迷能够为自己不同的收藏系列打造充满个性的展示架。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1911512768/sole-stacks-display-and-store-your-shoes-with-love\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，最低价为 75 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160731210857AiWk6VjQTRUPK0oD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.692647\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607312108575jaPQNoZ9TAvzbSB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.692647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160731210857aQznjONLw4UeAud1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.692647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607312108581gBRMrAEWfpjyeho.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}